{"article_id":"tpX028czJDmkMRGR","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"UPDATE :","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"A federal judge has ordered a defiant Kentucky clerk to jail","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"after she refused to issue marriage licenses to gay couples .","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"U.S. District Judge David Bunning told Rowan County Clerk Kim Davis","depth":9},{"id":4,"text":"she would be jailed","depth":10},{"id":5,"text":"until she complied with his order","depth":11},{"id":6,"text":"to issue the licenses .","depth":11},{"id":7,"text":"Davis said","depth":11},{"id":8,"text":"`` thank you ''","depth":11},{"id":9,"text":"before she was led out of the courtroom by a U.S. marshal .","depth":10},{"id":10,"text":"She was not in handcuffs .","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"Bunning also warned deputy clerks around the state","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"that they could suffer the same fate","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"should they refuse to issue marriage licenses to gay couples .","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"Davis has refused to issue marriages licenses for two months","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"since the Supreme Court legalized gay marriage .","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"She argues","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"that her Christian faith should exempt her from signing the licenses .","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"I ' m very steadfast in what I believe .","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"I don ' t leave my conscience and my Christian soul out in my vehicle","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"and come in here","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"and pretend to be something","depth":11},{"id":22,"text":"I ' m not .","depth":11},{"id":23,"text":"It ' s easy to talk the talk ,","depth":6},{"id":24,"text":"but can you walk the walk ?","depth":6},{"id":25,"text":"- Kim Davis , clerk of Rowan County , Kentucky Liberty Counsel attorney Mat Staver ,","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"who is representing Davis ,","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"called the ruling \" outrageous . \"","depth":6},{"id":28,"text":"\" If this country has come to this point","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"where a judge jails someone like Kim Davis for their religious convictions -","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"then we have lost our religious liberty , \"","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"Staver told me .","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"He said","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"Davis will be fingerprinted and photographed \" just like a criminal . \"","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"\" This can not be tolerated , \"","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"he said .","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"\" This is ultimately going to spark a huge debate around the country .","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"This is not the kind of country","depth":6},{"id":38,"text":"-","depth":6},{"id":39,"text":"this is not the America","depth":6},{"id":40,"text":"that our founders envisioned . \"","depth":6},{"id":41,"text":"Kim Davis could become the first Christian in America","depth":5},{"id":42,"text":"jailed","depth":5},{"id":43,"text":"as a result of the Supreme Court decision","depth":5},{"id":44,"text":"legalizing gay marriage .","depth":5},{"id":45,"text":"\" I ' ve weighed the cost","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"and I ' m prepared to go to jail ,","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"I sure am , \"","depth":6},{"id":48,"text":"Mrs. Davis told me in an exclusive interview .","depth":5},{"id":49,"text":"\" This has never been a gay or lesbian issue for me .","depth":6},{"id":50,"text":"This is about upholding the word of God . \"","depth":6},{"id":51,"text":"\" This is a heaven or hell issue for me and for every other Christian","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"that believes , \"","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"she said .","depth":7},{"id":54,"text":"\" This is a fight","depth":7},{"id":55,"text":"worth fighting . \"","depth":7},{"id":56,"text":"Davis is the clerk of Rowan County , Ky.","depth":7},{"id":57,"text":"- a small patch of earth in the northeastern part of the state .","depth":7},{"id":58,"text":"She was elected last November","depth":7},{"id":59,"text":"- taking the place of her mother ,","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"who held the position for nearly 40 years .","depth":8},{"id":61,"text":"It ' s fair to say that issuing marriage licenses was something of a family business -","depth":6},{"id":62,"text":"until the day","depth":7},{"id":63,"text":"the Supreme Court legalized gay marriage .","depth":7},{"id":64,"text":"Davis is a devout Apostolic Christian ,","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"and she knew","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"that","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"should gay marriage become legal ,","depth":12},{"id":68,"text":"she could not","depth":13},{"id":69,"text":"and would not sign her name on a same-sex marriage certificate .","depth":13},{"id":70,"text":"\" I would have to either make a decision","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"to stand","depth":12},{"id":72,"text":"or I would have to buckle down","depth":13},{"id":73,"text":"and leave , \"","depth":13},{"id":74,"text":"she said ,","depth":11},{"id":75,"text":"pondering her choices .","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"\" And","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"if I left ,","depth":12},{"id":78,"text":"resigned","depth":13},{"id":79,"text":"or chose to retire ,","depth":13},{"id":80,"text":"I would have no voice for God ' s word .","depth":11},{"id":81,"text":"So","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"when that day came ,","depth":11},{"id":83,"text":"she issued an edict :","depth":11},{"id":84,"text":"No more marriage licenses would be issued in Rowan County .","depth":9},{"id":85,"text":"It was a decision","depth":10},{"id":86,"text":"that would bring down the wrath of militant LGBT activists and their supporters .","depth":10},{"id":87,"text":"\" They told my husband","depth":12},{"id":88,"text":"they were going to burn us down","depth":13},{"id":89,"text":"while we slept in our home , \"","depth":13},{"id":90,"text":"she said .","depth":11},{"id":91,"text":"\" He ' s been told","depth":11},{"id":92,"text":"that he would be beaten up","depth":13},{"id":93,"text":"and tied up","depth":14},{"id":94,"text":"and made to watch them rape me .","depth":14},{"id":95,"text":"I have been told","depth":13},{"id":96,"text":"that gays should kill me . \"","depth":13},{"id":97,"text":"Liberty Counsel , the public interest law firm","depth":11},{"id":98,"text":"that represents Davis ,","depth":11},{"id":99,"text":"says","depth":10},{"id":100,"text":"forcing her to issue same-sex marriage licenses violates her religious beliefs .","depth":9},{"id":101,"text":"But the courts don ' t seem interested in that argument .","depth":9},{"id":102,"text":"A federal judge ordered her to issue the licenses ,","depth":10},{"id":103,"text":"an appeals court upheld that decision","depth":11},{"id":104,"text":"and the U.S. Supreme Court declined to intervene .","depth":11},{"id":105,"text":"Should Davis continue to defy the law ,","depth":8},{"id":106,"text":"she could be fined or sent to jail .","depth":8},{"id":107,"text":"No matter what the court decides ,","depth":7},{"id":108,"text":"Davis says","depth":9},{"id":109,"text":"she will not violate her religious beliefs","depth":9},{"id":110,"text":"-","depth":9},{"id":111,"text":"and she will not resign her post .","depth":9},{"id":112,"text":"\" I ' m very steadfast in what I believe , \"","depth":9},{"id":113,"text":"she told me .","depth":9},{"id":114,"text":"\" I don ' t leave my conscience and my Christian soul out in my vehicle","depth":9},{"id":115,"text":"and come in here","depth":10},{"id":116,"text":"and pretend to be something","depth":11},{"id":117,"text":"I ' m not .","depth":11},{"id":118,"text":"It ' s easy to talk the talk ,","depth":8},{"id":119,"text":"but can you walk the walk ? \"","depth":8},{"id":120,"text":"The mainstream media and the activists have been ruthless .","depth":6},{"id":121,"text":"They ' ve portrayed her as a monster - a right-wing , homophobic hypocrite .","depth":8},{"id":122,"text":"She ' s been smeared by tabloid-style reports on her checkered past .","depth":10},{"id":123,"text":"They ' ve written extensively about her failed marriages .","depth":10},{"id":124,"text":"It ' s true ,","depth":10},{"id":125,"text":"she ' s been married four times .","depth":10},{"id":126,"text":"But what ' s missing in the mainstream media coverage is the context .","depth":7},{"id":127,"text":"Her life was radically changed by Jesus Christ in 2011 ,","depth":7},{"id":128,"text":"and since then she has become a different person .","depth":7},{"id":129,"text":"\" My God in heaven knows every crack , every crevice , every deep place in my heart , \"","depth":10},{"id":130,"text":"she said .","depth":10},{"id":131,"text":"\" And he knows the thoughts","depth":11},{"id":132,"text":"that are in my mind","depth":11},{"id":133,"text":"before I even think them .","depth":10},{"id":134,"text":"And he has given me such a beautiful and wonderful grace through all of this . \"","depth":8},{"id":135,"text":"She once lived for the devil ,","depth":10},{"id":136,"text":"but now she lives for God .","depth":10},{"id":137,"text":"She ' s a sinner","depth":10},{"id":138,"text":"saved by grace .","depth":10},{"id":139,"text":"\" I had created such a pit of sin for myself with my very own hands , \"","depth":9},{"id":140,"text":"she told me .","depth":9},{"id":141,"text":"So how does she handle the reporters and talking heads","depth":6},{"id":142,"text":"who call her a hypocrite ?","depth":6},{"id":143,"text":"\" All","depth":8},{"id":144,"text":"I can say to them","depth":8},{"id":145,"text":"is","depth":8},{"id":146,"text":"if they have a sordid past like what I had ,","depth":11},{"id":147,"text":"they too can receive the cleansing","depth":12},{"id":148,"text":"and renewing ,","depth":12},{"id":149,"text":"and they can start a fresh life","depth":11},{"id":150,"text":"and they can be different , \"","depth":11},{"id":151,"text":"she said .","depth":9},{"id":152,"text":"\" They don ' t have to remain in their sin ,","depth":7},{"id":153,"text":"there ' s hope for tomorrow . \"","depth":7},{"id":154,"text":"Davis did not seek the national spotlight .","depth":3},{"id":155,"text":"She had no intention","depth":5},{"id":156,"text":"of becoming a spokeswoman for religious liberty ,","depth":5},{"id":157,"text":"and she bristles at the idea","depth":6},{"id":158,"text":"that she is a hero of the faith .","depth":6},{"id":159,"text":"\" I ' m just a vessel","depth":10},{"id":160,"text":"God has chosen","depth":10},{"id":161,"text":"for this time and this place , \"","depth":9},{"id":162,"text":"she said .","depth":8},{"id":163,"text":"\" I ' m no different than any other Christian .","depth":7},{"id":164,"text":"It was my appointed time","depth":8},{"id":165,"text":"to stand ,","depth":8},{"id":166,"text":"and their time will come . \"","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":333,"left":222,"right":332,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":222,"left":207,"right":221,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":207,"left":191,"right":206,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":191,"left":180,"right":190,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":180,"left":0,"right":179,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":179,"left":168,"right":178,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":168,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":178,"left":175,"right":177,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":175,"left":171,"right":174,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":171,"left":3,"right":170,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":170,"left":4,"right":169,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":169,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":174,"left":173,"right":10,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":173,"left":172,"right":9,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":172,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":177,"left":11,"right":176,"relati